:"有衝突咩肥婆都唔係女人"},{"pid":"c25d3555b43d1c80eaac3388612c7de3707a9cdf","tid":354600,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/183339_008b823d5d4a3e6220817633f8d8de8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F183339_008b823d5d4a3e6220817633f8d8de8f.jpg&h=c0b42359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁佢香定臭？"},{"pid":"a4863c87aa1e81047a22d5460f7e84cf64f4576a","tid":354600,"uid":78614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/183339_008b823d5d4a3e6220817633f8d8de8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F183339_008b823d5d4a3e6220817633f8d8de8f.jpg&h=c0b42359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁佢香定臭？</blockquote><br />\n我都想索下佢陣味"},{"pid":"ac01650f1e6d9e475967b9bd12d2e36cea8f73cf","tid":354600,"uid":58604,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"正所謂色香味<br />\n見到色先會有香<br />\n香又會影響個味<br />\n有色繼而有香<br />\n無色何來會有人想知道佢香唔香<br />\n就算唔聞都知佢臭<br />\n<br />\n你係遠處見到舊屎或者垃圾車<br />\n未聞到都已經會捂住個鼻啦<br />\n何況肥婆呢種生物比屎比垃圾車更為污穢<br />\n<br />\n每個人獨有嘅祖傳染色體都會話比自己知<br />\n有得比我揀 一定唔會揀肥婆<br />\n係世世代代傳落黎<br />\n唔好同我講咩楊貴妃都好肥<br />\n你見過楊貴妃咩<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n肥婆臭係因為上一代上上一代<br />\n留比我地嘅智慧<br />\n比我地分辨到咩係肥咩係瘦<br />\n幫我地選擇個好嘅女人延續下一代<br />\n快啲絕種啦<br />\n死爛臭肥婆"},{"pid":"fde03946a3b9ef416e7109b5ea1f1c8491a5583e","tid":354600,"uid":78614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正所謂色香味<br />\n見到色先會有香<br />\n香又會影響個味<br />\n有色繼而有香<br />\n無色何來會有人想知道佢香唔香<br />\n就算唔聞都知佢臭<br />\n<br />\n你係遠處見到舊屎或者垃圾車<br />\n未聞到都已經會捂住個鼻啦<br />\n何況肥婆呢種生物比屎比垃圾車更為污穢<br />\n<br />\n每個人獨有嘅祖傳染色體都會話比自己知<br />\n有得比我揀 一定唔會揀肥婆<br />\n係世世代代傳落黎<br />\n唔好同我講咩楊貴妃都好肥<br />\n你見過楊貴妃咩<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n肥婆臭係因為上一代上上一代<br />\n留比我地嘅智慧<br />\n比我地分辨到咩係肥咩係瘦<br />\n幫我地選擇個好嘅女人延續下一代<br />\n快啲絕種啦<br />\n死爛臭肥婆</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64beac74755bd50e1d80043c28a992510a05a43c","tid":354600,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"因為我每次約佢佢都一定沖完涼先出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704a27835bf337f69df7021a3a98819e37362443","tid":354600,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇過一篇文,話如果你同果個人既基因係可以做到愈多互補,你聞到既體味就對你愈吸引(即係係你角度係香)<br />\n相反就會覺得臭</blockquote><br />\n即係我覺得肥婆臭時肥婆都覺得我好臭？</blockquote><br />\n可以話係,但又未必<br />\n可能你既基因可以令佢既基因結合得好,對佢有利,佢會覺得你香<br />\n但係你既角度其實無咩着數,所以你覺得佢臭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係咁<br />\n女士又會唔會聞到同佢DNA 夾嘅男士體香？？"},{"pid":"cc7a30664003249e9ff760925ba3355d5f44c1c8","tid":354600,"uid":58604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇過一篇文,話如果你同果個人既基因係可以做到愈多互補,你聞到既體味就對你愈吸引(即係係你角度係香)<br />\n相反就會覺得臭</blockquote><br />\n即係我覺得肥婆臭時肥婆都覺得我好臭？</blockquote><br />\n可以話係,但又未必<br />\n可能你既基因可以令佢既基因結合得好,對佢有利,佢會覺得你香<br />\n但係你既角度其實無咩着數,所以你覺得佢臭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係咁<br />\n女士又會唔會聞到同佢DNA 夾嘅男士體香？？</blockquote><br />\n好似話荷爾蒙有味<br />\n即係男人睪丸酮素越高越吸引女人<br />\n女人就越靚越香<br />\n因為唔靚唔會想聞"},{"pid":"e158f73f6bf889f60a7b61eec9c25d4a09712460","tid":354600,"uid":12351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"人體唔係冇香味咩"},{"pid":"3ff86e373d48fa6385e2a52f6e6e07d62f17160a","tid":354600,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"@龜頭小嘴"},{"pid":"4126bf515d904670b0e67ad1e71579de44ccf5ee","tid":354600,"uid":13900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"好似係食得肉多d汗會臭d"},{"pid":"de3bcf9ed22ffc529cf1f0fc483cf34d4eb432b5","tid":354600,"uid":78614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"比負皮果位肥婆可以入埋黎同我地理性討論下"},{"pid":"517f235799f019958488a44d7005d94dbdfb84be","tid":354600,"uid":78614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似係食得肉多d汗會臭d</blockquote><br />\n但有無話係咩肉？"},{"pid":"4259f121aeb25ee5602ccf5fa9d580e58ccb096d","tid":354600,"uid":21863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"鐘意榴連既，會覺得陣味香。 唔鐘意既，會覺得臭過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85c3451d65f161258297f87e23ab918a6e2c564","tid":354600,"uid":17945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"如果有個男人鐘意個肥婆 就算佢臭都會覺得係香"},