>如題 <span style=\"color: red;\">成日行街經過啲肥婆果陣硬</span>係聞到陣怪味<br />\n好撚想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其他女又好香 想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0913afe4bc96ab248b3009b1dc6e954248389aeb","tid":354600,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意榴連既，會覺得陣味香。 唔鐘意既，會覺得臭過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有人會鍾意肥婆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420340e8ed4c2e6c13618fb0ebc835fc79fece07","tid":354600,"uid":56791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鐘意榴連既，會覺得陣味香。 唔鐘意既，會覺得臭過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有人會鍾意肥婆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯賭就得啦<br />\n你睇下苟姑娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3e08045352a7e74e83bc3af88fb678d7229ecb","tid":354600,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"食太多肉"},{"pid":"7d8fd7a9faf1af49d4febfca8f5df1e53255b6b4","tid":354600,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我男朋友好認真咁答我<br />\n<br />\n因為肥婆唔運動，尿酸體內積累太多，一出汗尿酸同汗一齊排出體外，啲汗蒸發左淨返尿酸，所以好撚臭<br />\n<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁香點解釋"}]}